{"tid":337213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3渦旋恐混戰！南海低壓增強存變數 「鹿」死誰手？","createTime":"2017-07-27T06:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T05:08:05.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64ead8eb604e58e7a710cf0eb40685ca61d18534","tid":337213,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dtnxgry6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdtnxgry6&h=2924e9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港日前才送走迷你風暴「洛克」，南海未來數天再有低壓區發展，但因西北太平洋有另外兩股熱帶氣旋「納沙」和「奧鹿」，三個渦旋可能互相影響，令南海低壓區的發展和動向更添變數。天文台暫料本周五（28日）的天氣較不穩定，「大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨」，表明周五及周末實際天氣如何，「要視乎南海低壓區與菲律賓以東的納沙的發展及兩者的相互作用」。<br />\n<br />\n記者 李鈺廷<br />\n<br />\n天文台預計，南海中至北部的廣闊低壓槽會發展為低壓區，未來兩三日會繼續發展，而菲律賓以東的熱帶氣旋納沙則逐漸北移，趨向台灣以東海域。天文台指出，南海的潛在低壓區可能與納沙出現相互作用，其發展及動向存在不確定性。<br />\n<br />\n兩股低壓系統若相距太近，便可能互相影響各自的路徑和強度，學術上稱為「籐原效應」。天文台科學主任莊思寧回覆《蘋果》查詢時解釋，兩股低壓系統通常會圍繞它們的中間點，逆時針移動；過程中，較弱的低壓系統，強度或會被削弱，甚至被吞併<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57005088&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57005088%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170727&d=AnW0vIhbrWqWGH6Ax3axqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e3b523d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57005088%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170727&h=171a3dd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57005088&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170727</a>"},{"pid":"da9587faf7f8be20b494e993ebf7abf7fae4c886","tid":337213,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hcjd8p3n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhcjd8p3n&h=141bcb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時係遠d嗰個勁d"},{"pid":"3bee18c4998348b9db8b0f544d8991fc512a70e2","tid":337213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"1848ac43f05249d0c799bafef565b93efdc86c3c","tid":337213,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"仆你個街~我星期日飛台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc308ae5e881f6548ebdfc2c8e11149283bbbe3","tid":337213,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"納沙同奧鹿無咩可能啦。。。。<br />\n個距離差咁q遠"},{"pid":"3ea0ac5d0f69adc5a26d083de53aef518abc3175","tid":337213,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"星期一二打八號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b5884bf5d5396c4f21e1c933c0d3d9fa482e8e","tid":337213,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期一二打八號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講， 1，2難d  成到形都可能係六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9b4abf0cbeda8d3de30651bda6774bb2030747","tid":337213,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期一二打八號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要8號呀, 等星期六日天文台施捨俾你啦"},{"pid":"3bfe033d08837c2bf00d247f91a323e9682962f7","tid":337213,"uid":36429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆你個街~我星期日飛台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我星六飛台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969ef8e08dc131551d91ccfd7e52dde0bba2cf33","tid":337213,"uid":14758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:44:48.